Package: cccc
Title: Chronological Corpora Curve Clustering
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", email = "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for analyzing and visualizing the temporal evolution of terms in a corpus. 
    Includes methods for importing and normalizing term-document matrices, selecting and applying
    optimal smoothing splines, and plotting functional trends.
